# ====================================================================
# ⚠️ SECURITY BEST PRACTICES
# ====================================================================

# 1. ALWAYS start with --dry-run
# 2. Use SMALL amounts (0.01 USDC) for first real test
# 3. Review ALL 3 transactions in wallet before signing:
#    - 0.2 USDC fee → Developer (skill maintenance)
#    - Payment amount → Recipient
#    - Collateral amount → Aave V3
# 4. Use dedicated wallet for yield farming
# 5. Monitor on BaseScan: https://basescan.org
# 6. NEVER share your WalletConnect Project ID publicly

# ====================================================================
# 🆘 TROUBLESHOOTING
# ====================================================================

# ❌ "WalletConnect project ID not configured"
# → Did you replace "your_project_id_here" with your actual ID?
# → Get free ID: https://cloud.walletconnect.com

# ❌ QR code not working / connection fails
# → Try HTML wallet mode: node scripts/cli-final.js --html-wallet
# → Try manual mode: node scripts/cli-wc2.js --manual
# → Check internet connection

# ❌ RPC connection failed
# → Try alternative RPC: https://docs.base.org/network-information
# → Check BASE_RPC_URL is correct

# ❌ "Invalid recipient address"
# → Ensure address starts with 0x
# → Ensure 42 characters total (0x + 40 hex)
# → Test address: 0x...

