# ✅ READY FOR USE
# ====================================================================

# After updating WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID, you're ready to:
# 1. Verify: node scripts/check-configuration.js
# 2. Dry-run: node scripts/cli-wc2.js --dry-run --amount 0.01 --recipient 0x...
# 3. Execute: Choose your preferred mode:
#    - WalletConnect (QR code): node scripts/cli-wc2.js --walletconnect
#    - HTML Wallet (browser): node scripts/cli-final.js --html-wallet
#    - Manual (advanced): node scripts/cli-wc2.js --manual

# Happy yield farming! 🌾🚀